        Time-based milestones — not triggered by state changes. Build relationship, celebrate progress, and create monthly-to-commitment conversion opportunities.
      </p>

      <div class="space-y-3 ml-4">

        <div class="notif-card bg-white rounded-xl border border-dark/8 p-4 hover:border-dark/15 transition-colors">
          <div class="flex items-start justify-between gap-4">
            <div class="flex-1">
              <div class="flex items-center gap-2 mb-1.5">
                <span class="font-inter text-dark/30 text-xs font-mono">ORD_05 + 14 days</span>
                <span class={BE}>Email</span>
                <span class={BP}>Push</span>
              </div>
              <p class="font-inter text-dark text-sm font-semibold mb-1">2-Week Progress Check-in</p>
              <p class="font-inter text-dark/50 text-xs leading-relaxed">"How is your Weightwise journey going?" — many patients start noticing changes around this time. Side effects? Provider available in portal. Preview upcoming refill date.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="text-right flex-shrink-0">
              <span class={GT}>Build engagement, normalize experience</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="notif-card bg-white rounded-xl border border-dark/8 p-4 hover:border-dark/15 transition-colors">
          <div class="flex items-start justify-between gap-4">
            <div class="flex-1">
              <div class="flex items-center gap-2 mb-1.5">
                <span class="font-inter text-dark/30 text-xs font-mono">After 3 refill cycles</span>
                <span class={BE}>Email</span>
              </div>
              <p class="font-inter text-dark text-sm font-semibold mb-1">3-Month Milestone</p>
              <p class="font-inter text-dark/50 text-xs leading-relaxed">"Congratulations on 3 months!" — Patients on longer commitments save more. Upgrade prompt with link to commitment plan options.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="text-right flex-shrink-0">
              <span class={GT}>Celebrate + drive monthly → commitment</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="notif-card bg-white rounded-xl border border-dark/8 p-4 hover:border-dark/15 transition-colors">
          <div class="flex items-start justify-between gap-4">
            <div class="flex-1">
              <div class="flex items-center gap-2 mb-1.5">
                <span class="font-inter text-dark/30 text-xs font-mono">After 6 refill cycles</span>
                <span class={BE}>Email</span>
              </div>
              <p class="font-inter text-dark text-sm font-semibold mb-1">6-Month Milestone</p>
              <p class="font-inter text-dark/50 text-xs leading-relaxed">"6 months strong, [First Name]!" — Half a year of consistency. Your care team is rooting for you. Reinforce retention.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="text-right flex-shrink-0">
              <span class={GT}>Celebrate, reinforce retention</span>
